snippet.title: beatmania 2ndMIX (Arcade / 1998) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
beatmania 2ndMIX, emulated via MAME 0.182 (using the new PortAudio output module).

0:57 QUADRA - Beginning of Life "AMBIENT"
2:48 reo-nagumo - Do you love me? "BALLADE (JAZZ-SOUL)"
4:34 DJ BATTLE
5:55 NITE SYSTEM - LOVE SO GROOVY (Nite's After Luv mix) "HOUSE SPILITUAL MIX"
8:17 Crunky Boy - jam jam reggae (Funky Jam Cookie mix) "REGGAE FUNKY MIX"
10:10 DJ Mazinger - u gotta groove (Triple Mazin Dub) "HIP-HOP STREET MIX"
11:54 QUADRA - OVERDOSER (Driving Dub mix) "MINIMAL TECHNO MIX"
13:51 DJ FX - Acid Bomb "HARD TEKNO"
15:58 Credits
